TypeSignature.Value: .class public auto ansi beforefieldinit EntityEqualityRewritingExpressionVisitor extends System.Linq.Expressions.ExpressionVisitor

Docs.summary: Rewrites comparisons of entities (as opposed to comparisons of their properties) into comparison of their keys.
Docs.remarks: For example, an expression such as cs.Where(c => c == something) would be rewritten to cs.Where(c => c.Id == something.Id).
